  },
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Today, I will make a picture for Mom.",
      "zh": "今天，我要為媽媽畫一幅畫。",
      "ja": "今日はママのために絵を描くよ。",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "A very nice picture.",
      "zh": "一幅非常漂亮的畫。",
      "ja": "とても素敵な絵。",
      "time": "00:00:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mom will smile when she sees it.",
      "zh": "媽媽看到會笑的。",
      "ja": "ママは見たら笑うよ。",
      "time": "00:00:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe she will say Leo.",
      "zh": "也許她會說，Leo。",
      "ja": "きっと『レオ』って言うかも。",
      "time": "00:00:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This is amazing.",
      "zh": "這真是太棒了。",
      "ja": "すごいね。",
      "time": "00:00:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe she will give me a big hug.",
      "zh": "也許她會給我一個大大的擁抱。",
      "ja": "きっと大きなハグをしてくれるよ。",
      "time": "00:00:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay, I am ready now.",
      "zh": "好了，我準備好了。",
      "ja": "よし、準備できたよ。",
      "time": "00:00:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mom, Mom, look.",
      "zh": "媽媽，媽媽，看。",
      "ja": "ママ、ママ、見て。",
      "time": "00:00:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, Leo, not now, please.",
      "zh": "哦，Leo，現在不行，拜託。",
      "ja": "ああ、レオ、今はダメだよ。",
      "time": "00:00:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Just one minute.",
      "zh": "等一下。",
      "ja": "ちょっと待って。",
      "time": "00:00:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I am busy, honey.",
      "zh": "我很忙，親愛的。",
      "ja": "今忙しいの。",
      "time": "00:00:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I am working now.",
      "zh": "我正在工作。",
      "ja": "今仕事中なの。",
      "time": "00:00:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But I made it for you.",
      "zh": "可是我畫給你的。",
      "ja": "でもママのために描いたんだよ。",
      "time": "00:00:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I know, sweetie.",
      "zh": "我知道，寶貝。",
      "ja": "わかってるよ、かわいい子。",
      "time": "00:00:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Later, okay?",
      "zh": "等一下，好嗎？",
      "ja": "後でね。",
      "time": "00:00:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, okay.",
      "zh": "哦，好吧。",
      "ja": "うん、わかった。",
      "time": "00:00:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mr. Teddy.",
      "zh": "泰迪先生。",
      "ja": "テディさん。",
      "time": "00:00:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mom did not look.",
      "zh": "媽媽沒有看。",
      "ja": "ママは見てくれなかった。",
      "time": "00:00:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But maybe she is busy.",
      "zh": "但也許她很忙。",
      "ja": "でも多分忙しいんだ。",
      "time": "00:00:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That is okay.",
      "zh": "沒關係。",
      "ja": "大丈夫。",
      "time": "00:00:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I can wait.",
      "zh": "我可以等。",
      "ja": "待てるよ。",
      "time": "00:00:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "She will look later.",
      "zh": "她會之後看的。",
      "ja": "後で見てくれるよ。",
      "time": "00:00:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, later is okay.",
      "zh": "是的，之後也可以。",
      "ja": "うん、後でもいいよ。",
      "time": "00:00:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I will wait nicely.",
      "zh": "我會乖乖等。",
      "ja": "ちゃんと待つよ。",
      "time": "00:00:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hey, Leo, what do you have there?",
      "zh": "嘿，Leo，你那裡拿著什麼？",
      "ja": "ねえ、レオ、それ何持ってるの？",
      "time": "00:00:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "A picture for Mom.",
      "zh": "給媽媽的畫。",
      "ja": "ママのための絵だよ。",
      "time": "00:00:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Wow.",
      "zh": "哇。",
      "ja": "わあ。",
      "time": "00:01:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Can I see?",
      "zh": "我可以看嗎？",
      "ja": "見せてくれる？",
      "time": "00:01:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Not yet.",
      "zh": "還不行。",
      "ja": "まだだよ。",
      "time": "00:01:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It is for Mom first.",
      "zh": "這是先給媽媽的。",
      "ja": "これはまずママのためのもの。",
      "time": "00:01:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Ah, I see.",
      "zh": "啊，我懂了。",
      "ja": "ああ、そうか。",
      "time": "00:01:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Very secret.",
      "zh": "很秘密。",
      "ja": "とても秘密だね。",
      "time": "00:01:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Very secret.",
      "zh": "非常秘密。",
      "ja": "とっても秘密。",
      "time": "00:01:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Did Mom see it?",
      "zh": "媽媽看到了嗎？",
      "ja": "ママは見た？",
      "time": "00:01:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "沒有。",
      "ja": "いいえ。",
      "time": "00:01:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "She is busy.",
      "zh": "她很忙。",
      "ja": "忙しいんだ。",
      "time": "00:01:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Then show her later.",
      "zh": "那就之後給她看。",
      "ja": "じゃあ後で見せてあげて。",
      "time": "00:01:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:01:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I think she will love it.",
      "zh": "我覺得她會喜歡的。",
      "ja": "きっと気に入ってくれるよ。",
      "time": "00:01:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I think so too.",
      "zh": "我也這麼想。",
      "ja": "私もそう思う。",
      "time": "00:01:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mom, can you look now?",
      "zh": "媽媽，你現在可以看嗎？",
      "ja": "ママ、今見てくれる？",
      "time": "00:01:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sorry, Leo.",
      "zh": "抱歉，Leo。",
      "ja": "ごめんね、レオ。",
      "time": "00:01:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Not now.",
      "zh": "現在不行。",
      "ja": "今はダメ。",
      "time": "00:01:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Why not?",
      "zh": "為什麼不行？",
      "ja": "どうして？",
      "time": "00:01:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I am very tired today.",
      "zh": "我今天很累。",
      "ja": "今日はとても疲れているの。",
      "time": "00:01:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I need to finish this first.",
      "zh": "我得先完成這個。",
      "ja": "これを先に終わらせないと。",
      "time": "00:01:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "She said no again.",
      "zh": "她又說不行了。",
      "ja": "またダメって言われた。",
      "time": "00:01:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe my picture is not good.",
      "zh": "也許我的畫不好。",
      "ja": "僕の絵はよくないのかな。",
      "time": "00:01:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No, that is not true.",
      "zh": "不，那不是真的。",
      "ja": "違うよ、それは違う。",
      "time": "00:01:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My picture is good.",
      "zh": "我的畫很好。",
      "ja": "僕の絵はいいんだ。",
      "time": "00:01:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I worked very hard.",
      "zh": "我很努力畫的。",
      "ja": "一生懸命描いたんだ。",
      "time": "00:01:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And I made Mom very pretty.",
      "zh": "我讓媽媽變得很漂亮。",
      "ja": "ママをとてもきれいに描いたよ。",
      "time": "00:01:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "So why did she not look?",
      "zh": "那她為什麼不看呢？",
      "ja": "なのにどうして見てくれないの？",
      "time": "00:01:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe she is really very tired.",
      "zh": "也許她真的很累。",
      "ja": "多分本当に疲れているんだ。",
      "time": "00:01:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe I should wait more.",
      "zh": "也許我應該再等一會兒。",
      "ja": "もっと待ったほうがいいかな。",
      "time": "00:01:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "One minute.",
      "zh": "一分鐘。",
      "ja": "１分。",
      "time": "00:02:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Two minutes.",
      "zh": "兩分鐘。",
      "ja": "２分。",
      "time": "00:02:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Three minutes.",
      "zh": "三分鐘。",
      "ja": "３分。",
      "time": "00:02:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This is a long time.",
      "zh": "這是很長的時間。",
      "ja": "長い時間だね。",
      "time": "00:02:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mr. Teddy, do you think later is a long time?",
      "zh": "泰迪先生，你覺得『之後』是很長的時間嗎？",
      "ja": "テディさん、『後で』は長い時間だと思う？",
      "time": "00:02:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I think yes.",
      "zh": "我覺得是。",
      "ja": "うん、そう思う。",
      "time": "00:02:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe for Mom's, later is very, very long.",
      "zh": "也許對媽媽來說，『之後』是非常非常長。",
      "ja": "ママにとっては『後で』はとてもとても長いんだろうね。",
      "time": "00:02:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I am so tired today.",
      "zh": "我今天真的很累。",
      "ja": "今日は本当に疲れた。",
      "time": "00:02:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I cannot do this now.",
      "zh": "我現在做不了這個。",
      "ja": "今はこれができない。",
      "time": "00:02:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It is okay.",
      "zh": "沒關係。",
      "ja": "大丈夫。",
      "time": "00:02:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Take your time.",
      "zh": "慢慢來。",
      "ja": "ゆっくりしてね。",
      "time": "00:02:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Did you hear that?",
      "zh": "你聽到了嗎？",
      "ja": "聞こえた？",
      "time": "00:02:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mom said I cannot do this now.",
      "zh": "媽媽說我現在做不了這個。",
      "ja": "ママは『今はできない』って言った。",
      "time": "00:02:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe she means me.",
      "zh": "也許她是指我。",
      "ja": "多分僕のことだ。",
      "time": "00:02:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe she cannot do me now.",
      "zh": "也許她現在應付不了我。",
      "ja": "今は僕に対応できないのかも。",
      "time": "00:02:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe I am too much today.",
      "zh": "也許我今天太吵了。",
      "ja": "今日は僕がうるさすぎたのかな。",
      "time": "00:02:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe Mom does not love me today.",
      "zh": "也許媽媽今天不愛我了。",
      "ja": "ママは今日僕のことを愛してないのかも。",
      "time": "00:02:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Did I do something bad today?",
      "zh": "我今天做錯什麼了嗎？",
      "ja": "今日は何か悪いことした？",
      "time": "00:02:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "沒有。",
      "ja": "いいえ。",
      "time": "00:02:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I cleaned my toys.",
      "zh": "我整理了玩具。",
      "ja": "おもちゃを片付けたよ。",
      "time": "00:02:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I used my crayons nicely.",
      "zh": "我好好地用蠟筆畫畫。",
      "ja": "クレヨンもきれいに使った。",
      "time": "00:02:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I did not break anything.",
      "zh": "我沒有弄壞東西。",
      "ja": "何も壊してないよ。",
      "time": "00:02:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I even made a picture for Mom.",
      "zh": "我還畫了畫給媽媽。",
      "ja": "ママのために絵も描いた。",
      "time": "00:02:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "So why is she like this?",
      "zh": "那她為什麼會這樣？",
      "ja": "なのにどうしてこんな風なの？",
      "time": "00:02:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mr. Teddy, I feel bad.",
      "zh": "泰迪先生，我覺得很難過。",
      "ja": "テディさん、悲しいよ。",
      "time": "00:02:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I do not want to give her my picture now.",
      "zh": "我現在不想給她我的畫。",
      "ja": "今は絵を見せたくない。",
      "time": "00:02:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I will keep it.",
      "zh": "我會自己留著。",
      "ja": "自分で持っておくよ。",
      "time": "00:02:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe she does not want it.",
      "zh": "也許她不想要。",
      "ja": "多分欲しくないんだ。",
      "time": "00:02:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Come on Mr. Teddy.",
      "zh": "走吧，泰迪先生。",
      "ja": "さあ、テディさん。",
      "time": "00:03:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let us go to my room.",
      "zh": "我們去我的房間吧。",
      "ja": "僕の部屋に行こう。",
      "time": "00:03:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Leo, where are you going?",
      "zh": "Leo，你要去哪裡？",
      "ja": "レオ、どこに行くの？",
      "time": "00:03:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My room.",
      "zh": "我的房間。",
      "ja": "僕の部屋。",
      "time": "00:03:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do you want to play with me later?",
      "zh": "你以後想跟我玩嗎？",
      "ja": "後で一緒に遊ぶ？",
      "time": "00:03:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe.",
      "zh": "也許吧。",
      "ja": "多分ね。",
      "time": "00:03:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hmm.",
      "zh": "嗯。",
      "ja": "うーん。",
      "time": "00:03:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That was a sad maybe.",
      "zh": "那是個難過的也許。",
      "ja": "悲しい『多分』だね。",
      "time": "00:03:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Are you sure?",
      "zh": "你確定嗎？",
      "ja": "本当？",
      "time": "00:03:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:03:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mr. Teddy, I think Mom does not love me today.",
      "zh": "泰迪先生，我覺得媽媽今天不愛我了。",
      "ja": "テディさん、ママは今日僕のことを愛してないと思う。",
      "time": "00:03:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe tomorrow she will love me again.",
      "zh": "也許明天她會再愛我。",
      "ja": "多分明日はまた愛してくれる。",
      "time": "00:03:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But not today.",
      "zh": "但不是今天。",
      "ja": "でも今日は違う。",
      "time": "00:03:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I do not want to talk.",
      "zh": "我不想說話。",
      "ja": "話したくない。",
      "time": "00:03:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I just want to stay here.",
      "zh": "我只想待在這裡。",
      "ja": "ここにいたいだけ。",
      "time": "00:03:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Just me and you.",
      "zh": "只有我和你。",
      "ja": "僕と君だけ。",
      "time": "00:03:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Leo, can I come in?",
      "zh": "Leo，我可以進來嗎？",
      "ja": "レオ、入ってもいい？",
      "time": "00:03:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:03:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Why are you sitting here in the dark?",
      "zh": "你為什麼坐在這黑暗中？",
      "ja": "どうして暗いところに座ってるの？",
      "time": "00:03:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am okay.",
      "zh": "我沒事。",
      "ja": "大丈夫だよ。",
      "time": "00:03:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I do not think you are okay.",
      "zh": "我覺得你不太好。",
      "ja": "大丈夫じゃないと思う。",
      "time": "00:03:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Leo, please tell me.",
      "zh": "Leo，請告訴我。",
      "ja": "レオ、話してごらん。",
      "time": "00:03:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Dad, does Mom still love me?",
      "zh": "爸爸，媽媽還愛我嗎？",
      "ja": "パパ、ママはまだ僕のこと愛してる？",
      "time": "00:03:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What?",
      "zh": "什麼？",
      "ja": "え？",
      "time": "00:03:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Of course she does.",
      "zh": "當然愛。",
      "ja": "もちろんだよ。",
      "time": "00:03:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "不。",
      "ja": "違う。",
      "time": "00:03:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Why do you say that?",
      "zh": "你為什麼這麼說？",
      "ja": "どうしてそう言うの？",
      "time": "00:03:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "She did not look at my picture.",
      "zh": "她沒有看我的畫。",
      "ja": "僕の絵を見てくれなかった。",
      "time": "00:03:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I called her two times.",
      "zh": "我叫了她兩次。",
      "ja": "二回呼んだんだ。",
      "time": "00:03:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "She said not now.",
      "zh": "她說現在不行。",
      "ja": "今はダメって言った。",
      "time": "00:03:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "She said I am tired.",
      "zh": "她說她累了。",
      "ja": "疲れてるって言った。",
      "time": "00:03:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "She said I cannot do this now.",
      "zh": "她說她現在做不了這個。",
      "ja": "今はこれができないって。",
      "time": "00:04:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I think she means me.",
      "zh": "我覺得她是指我。",
      "ja": "僕のことを言ってると思う。",
      "time": "00:04:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I think she does not want me today.",
      "zh": "我覺得她今天不想要我。",
      "ja": "今日は僕を欲しくないと思う。",
      "time": "00:04:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I think she does not love me today.",
      "zh": "我覺得她今天不愛我。",
      "ja": "今日は僕のことを愛してないと思う。",
      "time": "00:04:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That is not true.",
      "zh": "那不是真的。",
      "ja": "それは違うよ。",
      "time": "00:04:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Then why did she not look?",
      "zh": "那她為什麼不看呢？",
      "ja": "じゃあどうして見なかったの？",
      "time": "00:04:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Mom is very busy today.",
      "zh": "媽媽今天很忙。",
      "ja": "ママは今日はとても忙しいの。",
      "time": "00:04:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But she always looks.",
      "zh": "但她通常都會看的。",
      "ja": "でもいつもは見てくれるよ。",
      "time": "00:04:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Today she did not look.",
      "zh": "今天她沒有看。",
      "ja": "今日は見てくれなかった。",
      "time": "00:04:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:04:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I know.",
      "zh": "我知道。",
      "ja": "わかってるよ。",
      "time": "00:04:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But tired is not the same as no love.",
      "zh": "但累跟不愛是不一樣的。",
      "ja": "でも疲れているのと愛していないのは違うよ。",
      "time": "00:04:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I do not know.",
      "zh": "我不知道。",
      "ja": "わからない。",
      "time": "00:04:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Adults can be tired and still love you.",
      "zh": "大人可以累了但還是愛你。",
      "ja": "大人は疲れていても愛していることがあるんだ。",
      "time": "00:04:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Really?",
      "zh": "真的嗎？",
      "ja": "本当？",
      "time": "00:04:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This is very, very nice.",
      "zh": "這真的很好。",
      "ja": "これはとてもいいね。",
      "time": "00:04:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But Mom did not see it.",
      "zh": "但媽媽沒有看到。",
      "ja": "でもママは見てくれなかった。",
      "time": "00:04:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Then let us help her see it.",
      "zh": "那我們幫她看看吧。",
      "ja": "じゃあ見せてあげよう。",
      "time": "00:04:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "不。",
      "ja": "いや。",
      "time": "00:04:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am scared.",
      "zh": "我害怕。",
      "ja": "怖いんだ。",
      "time": "00:04:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Are you scared Mom will say no again?",
      "zh": "你害怕媽媽又說不行嗎？",
      "ja": "ママにまたダメって言われるのが怖いの？",
      "time": "00:04:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:04:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Leo?",
      "zh": "Leo？",
      "ja": "レオ？",
      "time": "00:04:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Are you in your room?",
      "zh": "你在房間嗎？",
      "ja": "部屋にいる？",
      "time": "00:04:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "He is here.",
      "zh": "他在這裡。",
      "ja": "ここにいるよ。",
      "time": "00:04:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Can I come in?",
      "zh": "我可以進來嗎？",
      "ja": "入ってもいい？",
      "time": "00:04:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Leo, dad told me what happened.",
      "zh": "Leo，爸爸告訴我發生了什麼。",
      "ja": "レオ、パパから聞いたよ。",
      "time": "00:05:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You were sad today.",
      "zh": "你今天很難過。",
      "ja": "今日は悲しかったね。",
      "time": "00:05:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Because of me?",
      "zh": "因為我嗎？",
      "ja": "僕のせい？",
      "time": "00:05:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I think you two should talk.",
      "zh": "我覺得你們應該談談。",
      "ja": "二人で話したほうがいいよ。",
      "time": "00:05:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:05:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Leo, what is wrong?",
      "zh": "Leo，怎麼了？",
      "ja": "レオ、どうしたの？",
      "time": "00:05:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mom, do you still love me?",
      "zh": "媽媽，你還愛我嗎？",
      "ja": "ママ、まだ僕のこと愛してる？",
      "time": "00:05:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What?",
      "zh": "什麼？",
      "ja": "え？",
      "time": "00:05:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You did not look at my picture.",
      "zh": "你沒有看我的畫。",
      "ja": "僕の絵を見てくれなかった。",
      "time": "00:05:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You did not smile at me.",
      "zh": "你沒有對我笑。",
      "ja": "僕に笑ってくれなかった。",
      "time": "00:05:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You said not now.",
      "zh": "你說現在不行。",
      "ja": "今はダメって言った。",
      "time": "00:05:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I thought maybe you did not love me today.",
      "zh": "我以為你今天不愛我了。",
      "ja": "今日は僕のことを愛してないのかと思った。",
      "time": "00:05:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, Leo, no.",
      "zh": "哦，Leo，不是的。",
      "ja": "ああ、レオ、違うよ。",
      "time": "00:05:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That is not true.",
      "zh": "那不是真的。",
      "ja": "それは違うよ。",
      "time": "00:05:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I am so sorry.",
      "zh": "我很抱歉。",
      "ja": "ごめんね。",
      "time": "00:05:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I was busy.",
      "zh": "我很忙。",
      "ja": "忙しかったの。",
      "time": "00:05:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I was tired.",
      "zh": "我很累。",
      "ja": "疲れていたの。",
      "time": "00:05:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But I did not forget you.",
      "zh": "但我沒有忘記你。",
      "ja": "でもあなたのことは忘れていない。",
      "time": "00:05:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And I never stopped loving you.",
      "zh": "我從未停止愛你。",
      "ja": "そしてずっと愛しているよ。",
      "time": "00:05:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Never?",
      "zh": "從未？",
      "ja": "ずっと？",
      "time": "00:05:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Never.",
      "zh": "從未。",
      "ja": "ずっとだよ。",
      "time": "00:05:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I love you every day.",
      "zh": "我每天都愛你。",
      "ja": "毎日愛しているよ。",
      "time": "00:05:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I thought you were angry with me.",
      "zh": "我以為你生我的氣。",
      "ja": "怒っているのかと思った。",
      "time": "00:05:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No sweetheart.",
      "zh": "不，親愛的。",
      "ja": "違うよ、かわいい子。",
      "time": "00:05:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I was just tired.",
      "zh": "我只是累了。",
      "ja": "ただ疲れていただけ。",
      "time": "00:06:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sometimes moms are tired.",
      "zh": "有時媽媽會累。",
      "ja": "時々ママは疲れるの。",
      "time": "00:06:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But tired does not mean no love.",
      "zh": "但累不代表不愛。",
      "ja": "でも疲れているからって愛していないわけじゃない。",
      "time": "00:06:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "So you still love me today?",
      "zh": "所以你今天還是愛我？",
      "ja": "じゃあ今日も僕のこと愛してる？",
      "time": "00:06:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:06:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can I see your picture now?",
      "zh": "我現在可以看你的畫嗎？",
      "ja": "今絵を見せてくれる？",
      "time": "00:06:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "いいよ。",
      "time": "00:06:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, Leo.",
      "zh": "哦，Leo。",
      "ja": "ああ、レオ。",
      "time": "00:06:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This is beautiful.",
      "zh": "這真漂亮。",
      "ja": "きれいな絵だね。",
      "time": "00:06:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You really like it?",
      "zh": "你真的喜歡嗎？",
      "ja": "本当に気に入った？",
      "time": "00:06:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes, I do.",
      "zh": "是的，我喜歡。",
      "ja": "うん、好きだよ。",
      "time": "00:06:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Thank you, Leo.",
      "zh": "謝謝你，Leo。",
      "ja": "ありがとう、レオ。",
      "time": "00:06:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And I have something for you too.",
      "zh": "我也有東西給你。",
      "ja": "そして君にも何かあるよ。",
      "time": "00:06:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "For me?",
      "zh": "給我？",
      "ja": "僕に？",
      "time": "00:06:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:06:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What is it?",
      "zh": "是什麼？",
      "ja": "何？",
      "time": "00:06:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Close your eyes.",
      "zh": "閉上眼睛。",
      "ja": "目を閉じて。",
      "time": "00:06:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Now open them.",
      "zh": "現在睜開。",
      "ja": "今開けて。",
      "time": "00:06:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Cupcake.",
      "zh": "杯子蛋糕。",
      "ja": "カップケーキ。",
      "time": "00:06:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, for you.",
      "zh": "是的，給你。",
      "ja": "うん、君のため。",
      "time": "00:06:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "For me?",
      "zh": "給我？",
      "ja": "僕に？",
      "time": "00:06:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I wanted to give it to you later.",
      "zh": "我本來想晚點給你。",
      "ja": "後であげようと思ってた。",
      "time": "00:06:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But I got too busy.",
      "zh": "但我太忙了。",
      "ja": "でも忙しくなっちゃって。",
      "time": "00:06:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It is beautiful.",
      "zh": "它很漂亮。",
      "ja": "きれいだね。",
      "time": "00:06:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Like your picture?",
      "zh": "像你的畫嗎？",
      "ja": "君の絵みたい？",
      "time": "00:06:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:06:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "So are we okay now?",
      "zh": "那我們現在沒事了嗎？",
      "ja": "じゃあもう大丈夫？",
      "time": "00:06:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:07:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mama loves me.",
      "zh": "媽媽愛我。",
      "ja": "ママは僕を愛してる。",
      "time": "00:07:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Of course I do.",
      "zh": "當然愛。",
      "ja": "もちろんだよ。",
      "time": "00:07:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mom?",
      "zh": "媽媽？",
      "ja": "ママ？",
      "time": "00:07:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes, Leo.",
      "zh": "是的，Leo。",
      "ja": "うん、レオ。",
      "time": "00:07:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Next time.",
      "zh": "下次。",
      "ja": "次はね。",
      "time": "00:07:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can you look at my picture faster?",
      "zh": "你能快點看我的畫嗎？",
      "ja": "僕の絵をもっと早く見てくれる？",
      "time": "00:07:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:07:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Next time I will stop and look.",
      "zh": "下次我會停下來看。",
      "ja": "次はちゃんと立ち止まって見るね。",
      "time": "00:07:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Promise.",
      "zh": "答應你。",
      "ja": "約束する。",
      "time": "00:07:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Promise.",
      "zh": "答應你。",
      "ja": "約束するよ。",
      "time": "00:07:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:07:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can we eat the cupcake now?",
      "zh": "我們現在可以吃杯子蛋糕嗎？",
      "ja": "今カップケーキ食べていい？",
      "time": "00:07:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:07:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let us share it.",
      "zh": "我們一起分享吧。",
      "ja": "一緒に食べよう。",
      "time": "00:07:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Me?",
      "zh": "我？",
      "ja": "僕？",
      "time": "00:07:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You?",
      "zh": "你？",
      "ja": "君？",
      "time": "00:07:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Dad?",
      "zh": "爸爸？",
      "ja": "パパ？",
      "time": "00:07:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And Mr. Teddy too.",
      "zh": "還有泰迪先生也一起。",
      "ja": "そしてテディさんもね。",
